thread.title: BRIEF-TICC Estimates Net Investment Income $0.14 Per Share-$0.16 Per Share For Q4​

author: Reuters Editorial
title: BRIEF-TICC Estimates Net Investment Income $0.14 Per Share-$0.16 Per Share For Q4​
text:
Feb 1 (Reuters) - TICC Capital Corp:
* TICC ANNOUNCES SELECTED PRELIMINARY ESTIMATED RESULTS FOR Q4 2017
* TICC CAPITAL - ESTIMATES CORE NET INVESTMENT INCOME FOR QUARTER ENDED DEC 31, 2017 WILL FALL WITHIN RANGE OF ABOUT $0.15 - $0.19 PER SHARE
* TICC CAPITAL CORP - ‍ ESTIMATES ITS NET ASSET VALUE AS OF DECEMBER 31, 2017 TO BE IN RANGE OF $7.50 TO $7.60 PER SHARE​
* TICC CAPITAL CORP - ‍ ESTIMATED NET INVESTMENT INCOME $0.14 PER SHARE - $0.16 PER SHARE FOR Q4​ Source text for Eikon: Further company coverage:
